data.description: Provide a JSON dictionary of keys/value pairs to be updated with the keys determined by the response from the "Get Template Field Names" method

Authenticates access to the API. IMPORTANT: You will need to pair your PassKit API Key and Secret with your Mashape username BEFORE you can use this or any other method via mashape.  To do this, use a browser to visit https://api.passkit.com/v1/mashape/{mashape username} (replace {mashape username} with your username); 2. Authenticate with your PassKit API KEY and API SECRET; if you are successful then you will receive a JSON response in your browser window, then you can test everything is working by clicking the "Test Endpoint" button for this method.  For more info: https://code.google.com/p/passkit/wiki/Authenticate
